Weather Web App

This is a weather web app built using HTML, CSS, and Javascript. It uses the OpenWeathermap API to fetch real-time weather data for any city in the world. The app is simple and easy to use, and it provides users with all the essential weather information, including:

Current temperature and humidity
Wind speed and direction
Atmospheric pressure
Cloud cover
Sunrise and sunset times
Hourly and daily forecasts
To use the app, simply enter the name of the city you want to view the weather for in the search bar and press enter. The app will then fetch the latest weather data and display it on the screen.

Features:

Real-time weather data for any city in the world
Simple and easy to use interface
Hourly and daily forecasts
Customizable temperature unit (Celsius or Fahrenheit)
Requirements:

Web browser with JavaScript enabled
